Namespace Jabra.NET.Sdk.Modules.RemoteMMI.Types

Interfaces

IRemoteMmi

Control a device's "MMI" (Man-Machine Interface) from the "remote host".

The "Man-Machine Interface" of a device are basically its buttons and its LEDs, while the "remote host" is simply the application on the PC.

IRemoteMmiEvent

An interaction with the device's man-machine interface (MMI). Mostly used for button presses.

Enums

Led

One of the LEDs on the device

LedBlinkingInterval

The blinking interval of an LED.

LedColor

The color an LED can have.

RemoteMmiEventType

A possible type of interaction with a device's man-machine interface (MMI). Mostly used for buttons.
